metadata.name: #1 / Speed
metadata.description: Speed is the pulse of motion, the rhythm of velocity. It's the rush of wind through your hair, the blur of scenery flashing by, the surge of adrenaline as you accelerate towards your destination. Whether racing towards a goal or leisurely strolling through life, speed sets the tone and pace of our journey. It can convey energy, excitement, and urgency, or a sense of calm and relaxation. Speed is the beat that keeps us moving forward, and the tempo that shapes our existence.
